B.ae_=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_bash","Bash","[Reaction] During your or ally turns, Make Status Check vs Str targeting an enemy range 1. On Success, deal weapon damage and apply your technique then knock the target prone. The target cannot make opportunity attacks until it is no longer prone.",B.S,B.d2)
B.ae6=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Impaling","Impaling","[Reaction] After you Succeed on a Melee Attack, spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Str. On Success give the target {Source} d6 bleed and dash the target to a free space in reach of your weapon and the target is restrained and moves with you until the start of your next turn. If your Impaled Target dies, you may Make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting an enemy range {Source}. On Success, fling the body at them deals {Source d12} damage. On Problems, the body lands adjacent to the target.",B.S,B.d2)
B.adW=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Vanguard","Vanguard","[Reaction] when an enemy starts or moves into your Melee Weapon\u2019s reach, spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack. On Success, deal weapon damage and the target is restrained until the end of their turn.",B.S,B.d2)
B.ae3=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Spin","Spin","[Reaction] after making a melee attack or during an allies turn, spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting enemies within 1. On success deal your weapons damage. If your weapon has reach, target enemies within 2 instead.",B.S,B.d2)
B.ae7=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Thrown","Thrown","[Reaction] During your turn, make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting an enemy range 3. On Problems your weapon lands in a space adjacent to the target. On success, the weapon is impaled. While impaled, the target moves at half speed. As an [Action] or a [Reaction] during your turn, make a Melee attack vs Str targeting an impaled enemy range 1. On Success, the target takes weapon damage, gains {Source} d6 bleed and then is knocked prone.  On problems, gain the weapon and the target gains {Source} d6 bleed. The target may spend an Action or reaction to pull out the weapon, Make a Status check vs Vit. On success, they gain {Source} d6 bleed and remove the weapon. On problems they gain {Half Source} d6 bleed and remove the weapon. If your weapon is impaled in a dead character your size or less, when range 1 during your turn, spend an [Action] or [reaction], make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting an enemy range 3. On success, gain your weapon and fling the body at the enemy dealing {Source d12} damage. On problems, the body lands adjacent to the target and the target has +1 to attacks against you.",B.S,B.d2)
