B.ae4=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_offhand","Offhand","[Reaction] During your or ally turns, you may spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack with a one handed weapon you are holding against an enemy in range using its weapon technique.",B.S,B.bX)
B.ae0=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Dueler","Dueler","[Reaction], When you succeed on a Melee Attack, Spend your reaction and the target has disadvantage on attacks that don\u2019t include you and you have disadvantage on attacks that don\u2019t include the target. You and the Target get a +1 to defense results from characters not involved in the duel. This lasts until one of you dies, the situation ends, or you duel another character. When you stop a duel by dueling another, any targets no longer dueled by you gain +1 to attacks against you until the end of their next turn.",B.S,B.bX)
B.aeb=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Backup","Backup","[Reaction], When you start your turn, you may spend your Reaction, and target an enemy in your weapons range and make a technique Attack. On Success, Push the target {Source} and they may not target you with opportunity attacks until the end of your turn.",B.S,B.bX)
B.ae5=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Dancer","Dancer","[Reaction], after succeeding a defense or during an allies turn, you may spend your reaction to dash {Half Source} then make a technique attack.",B.S,B.bX)
B.adV=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Throw","Throw","[Reaction] During an enemies turn when they are range 3, spend your reaction and make a Ranged Attack vs Dex. On problems, your weapon lands in a space adjacent to the target. On success, the weapon is impaled in the target, and while impaled, you and your allies have +1 to range attacks against the target. For each weapon impaled, the target gets a -1 penalty to speed. The target or an adjacent creature can pull out all the impaled weapons as an item interaction and the target gains {Source} d6 bleed per weapon. Passive, you have a total of {Half Level} extra of these weapons each situation and each time you use a supply to restock.",B.S,B.bX)
B.ae=new A.fz(1,"ranged")
B.adX=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_aim","Aim","At the start of your turn, spend your reaction. You gain +1 to attack results with ranged weapons and {Source/3} bonus range to all range weapon attacks until you move or dash Half your speed or more on a turn.",B.ae,B.d2)
B.aea=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Suppression","Suppression","[Reaction] When you Succeed on a Ranged Attack, Target a {Half Source} radius that contains at least 1 of the targets and make a Status Check vs Dex. On Success deal {Source d8} and all targets speed is reduced by {Half Source} until the end of their next turn.",B.ae,B.d2)
B.ae1=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Bayonet","Bayonet","[Reaction] During your turn, make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting 1 enemy range 2. On success, give the target {Source} d6 bleed, knock the target prone and the target may not make opportunity attacks against you until the end of your turn.",B.ae,B.d2)
B.adY=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_quick_shot","Quick Shot","[Reaction] Start of an enemy turn who is in range of your one handed ranged, spend your reaction and make a Ranged attack against the triggering enemy. On Success, deal weapon damage and you and your allies have a +1 to defenses caused by the target.",B.ae,B.bX)
B.ae2=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_offhand_ranged","Offhand","[Reaction] During your or ally turns, you may spend your reaction and make a Ranged Attack with a one handed weapon you are holding against an enemy in range using its weapon technique.",B.ae,B.bX)
B.ae8=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Rooten_Tooten","Rooten Tooten","[Reaction] At the end of an enemy turn who is in your weapon\u2019s range, make a Ranged Attack. On Success, deal the weapons damage and force the target to move {Half Source}. On problems, you may force them to move {Half Source} as long as this doesn't cause collision or direct harm. ",B.ae,B.bX)
B.ae9=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Gun_Fu","Gun Fu","[Reaction] During your turn or when an enemy becomes range 1, spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting that enemy or an enemy range 1. On Success, deal your weapon damage to the target, then dash {Half Source} spaces to a free space.",B.ae,B.bX)
B.adZ=new A.bF("weapon_reaction_Plan_B","Plan B","[Reaction] at the start of your turn if there are no enemies within short range of your weapon, Spend your reaction, target an enemy within long range of your weapon and make a Status Check vs Dex, On Success deal weapon damage with a source value of {Half Source} and until the end of your turn gain bonus speed equal to the short range of your weapon. ",B.ae,B.bX)
