B.Od=new A.a8("feature_corrosion","Corrosion","[Action]: Make a Melee Attack vs Int targeting 1 enemy Range 3. On Success, the target gains {Source} d6 Burn vs Int. While the target has this burn you and your allies ignore the target\u2019s damage resistance and shield.\n\n[Reaction] During your or ally turns, make a Melee attack vs Int targeting enemies range 1. On success, give the targets {Source} d6 Burn vs Int. While the target has this burn you and your allies ignore the target's damage resistance and shield.",B.r,B.Tc,!1)
B.Ij=new A.i("feature_eye_of_the_storm_combo_breeze","Combo Breeze","While concentrating, [Reaction] After the target succeeds with a melee attack, you may spend your reaction to make the Eye of the Storm Status Check against the enemy with a +1 bonus to success.")
