B.Oh=new A.a8("feature_eye_of_the_storm","Eye of the Storm","[Action] Target 1 creature you can see. As long as you remain concentrating, the first time an enemy starts or becomes {Source} spaces of the target during their turn, make a Status Check vs Str. On Success, deal {Source} d6 damage and push them {Source} spaces away. While concentrating, if you activate the ability again, you add the target to your concentration.\n\n[Reaction] During an ally\u2019s turn who is range 3, spend your reaction and begin concentrating on Eye of the Storm targeting that ally.",B.T,B.VL,!1)
B.M7=new A.i("feature_fae_step_group_step","Group Step","When you teleport, you may bring any adjacent allies with you to a free space adjacent to your destination.")
B.Mi=new A.i("feature_fae_step_glitter_in_the_eye","Glitter in the Eye","On success, you have advantage on defenses caused by the targets until the start of your next turn.")
B.LE=new A.i("feature_fae_step_sleepy_step","Sleepy Step","On success, enemies targeted have their speed reduced by {Half Source} and disadvantage on checks when using their reaction until the start of your next turn.")
B.WG=s([B.M7,B.Mi,B.LE],t.U)
B.Om=new A.a8("feature_fae_step","Fae Step","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Cha targeting each enemy range 1. On a Success, deal {Source d8} damage. Regardless, you may then teleport up to {Source} spaces to a free space.\n\n[Reaction] When an enemy becomes adjacent to you, spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack vs Cha. On Success, deal {Source d8} and teleport up to {Source} spaces to a free space.",B.r,B.WG,!1)
B.MN=new A.i("feature_firestorm_inferno","Inferno","While Concentrating: During your turn, spend your [Reaction] Make an Status Check vs Dex. On Success, Deal {Source d6} damage to each enemy in the zone.")
B.JY=new A.i("feature_firestorm_triple_storm","Triple Storm","When you use the action, Instead of targeting 1 area, instead target 3 one space radius areas instead. When you move the storm, move all 3 but you still may never affect an enemy more than once.")
