B.NK=new A.a8("feature_firestorm","Firestorm","[Action] Target a 2 space area Range 8, as long as you remain concentrating. Whenever a character starts their turn in the area or enters it for the first time during their turn, Make a Status Check vs Dex, On Success, ignite them dealing {Source d6} Damage and giving them {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Wis.\nWhile concentrating, During your turn you may spend your [Reaction] to move the zone {Power} spaces, moving does trigger the Effect on characters it passes over but never more than once.\n\n[Reaction] When you Succeed on an attack, Spend your reaction and place your firestorm so that at least 1 space of one of the targets of the triggering attack are in the firestorm.",B.r,B.VS,!1)
B.Lz=new A.i("feature_flight_flighty","Flighty","While concentrating, [Reaction] When you are targeted by an attack, you may spend your reaction to dash {Source} spaces. If the enemy can no longer target you with the ability, it automatically fails and doesn\u2019t affect you.")
B.J2=new A.i("feature_flight_lookout","Lookout","While concentrating, [Reaction] When an ally you can see makes a defense roll, you may spend your reaction before they roll to give them advantage.")
B.JN=new A.i("feature_flight_raptor","Raptor","While concentrating, At the end of your turn, pick an enemy in the initiative. On your next turn, Whenever you succeed on a melee attack targeting the target, give them {Half Source} d6 bleed.")
B.V3=s([B.Lz,B.J2,B.JN],t.U)
B.Ow=new A.a8("feature_flight","Flight","[Reaction] During your turn or at the start of the combat round, you begin concentrating on flying. While concentrating, you gain {Source} bonus speed, you dash instead of moving, and may fly vertically while moving. You must be on the ground or use a free space on the ground for the origin of any abilities or weapon attacks. You must end your turn in a free space on the ground.\n\n[Action] Begin concentrating on Flight.",B.T,B.V3,!1)
B.JI=new A.i("feature_fury_bloodlust","Bloodlust","During your fury, whenever you kill an enemy, you may make a fury attack as a free action.")
B.HC=new A.i("feature_fury_rage","Rage","You resist damage from the target of your last fury attack. You have advantage on concentration checks caused by the target of your last Fury Attack.")
B.IP=new A.i("feature_fury_pissed_off","Pissed Off","Whenever you fail a fury attack, you deal 1d12 extra damage on your next successful fury attack up to a max of {Source d12}.")
