B.OB=new A.a8("feature_fury","Fury","[Action] As long as you remain concentrating, when you activate this and the first time you fail an attack or defense each round, dash {Half Source} then make a Melee Attack vs Str. On success, deal {Source d12} damage. You still make the attack even if you fail the concentration check for fury.\n\n[Reaction] After failing a defense, you may spend your reaction, make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting an enemy range 1. On success deal {Source d12} damage and begin concentrating on your fury.",B.r,B.WJ,!1)
B.I2=new A.i("feature_gale_gust","Gust","All creatures in the encounter not targeted including you, are dashed half the distance in the same direction.")
B.MD=new A.i("feature_gale_wind_heeled","Wind Heeled","After using the action, you gain {Half Source} speed and dash instead of moving until the end of your turn. After using the reaction, the origin character gains {Half Source} speed and dash instead of moving until the end of their turn.")
B.Lx=new A.i("feature_gale_tornado","Tornado","You may have targeted enemies all dash the same distance away from the center of the ability or the origin character instead. Destroy walls and barriers created by skills or abilities in the area of the action.")
