B.ON=new A.a8("feature_gale","Gale","[Action] Target a 1 space radius Range 6, and range Attack every enemy there vs Wis. On Success, they take {Source d8} damage and you may force all creatures in the area to dash the same distance in the same direction up to {Source} spaces.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally range 6 succeeds with an attack during their turn, dash the triggering character and all the targets of the triggering attack {Source} spaces in the same direction.",B.r,B.T9,!1)
B.MY=new A.i("feature_gate_security","Security","Enemies may not enter your gates and enemies in range to enter your gates take {Half Source d6} extra damage when attacked.")
B.MU=new A.i("feature_gate_static_generator","Static Generator","When you or an ally travels through a gate for the first time on their turn, they gain {Source d6} shield.")
