B.OY=new A.a8("feature_gate","Gate","[Action] Target 2 free spaces Range {Source}, and summon gates in those spaces. Gates are considered barriers. Characters can move from a space adjacent to 1 gate to a free space adjacent to another gate for 1 space of movement. You may activate this later to instead create 1 gate and add it to the existing network of gates.\n\n[Reaction] During your or ally turns, spend your reaction and target an ally range {Source} and teleport them to a free space adjacent to you or one of your gates.",B.T,B.Wh,!1)
