B.NR=new A.a8("feature_ghost","Ghost","[Action] Target yourself or an ally range 1. The target slips into a shadowy form. Until the Start of your next turn, the target may move through enemies, does not provoke attacks of opportunity, they ignore difficult terrain, gain {Source} bonus speed, and they resist all damage that targets Str, Dex, or Vit.\n\n[Reaction] Start of any Turn, Spend your reaction, dash {Source} and until the start of your next turn, resist all damage that targets Str, Dex, Vit.",B.T,B.UV,!1)
