B.IL=new A.i("feature_grappling_hook_scoop","Scoop","When you target through an ally's space, you may bring those allies along, dashing them to a free space adjacent to your destination. If you pull an enemy through an ally, they ride the enemy and instead dash to a free space adjacent to the enemy.")
