B.I1=new A.i("feature_grappling_hook_swing","Swing","On Success, instead of dashing to the space, you may dash in a circle staying the same distance from the target space. You may dash to any point on the circle. If you have scoop, you scoop allies you swing into. If you have trip, you may trip enemies you swing into.")
