B.O5=new A.a8("feature_grappling_hook","Grappling Hook","Grappling Hook Away [Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting a free space range {2 + Source}. On success, dash to that space.\n\nHook [Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting an enemy range {2 + Source}. On success, deal {Source d8} damage and pull the target to a space adjacent.\n\n[Reaction] Start of a Turn, Spend your reaction and make a Ranged Attack targeting either a free space range {2+Source}, or an enemy range {2+Source}. On Success, either dash to the space, or deal {Source d8} damage and pull the target adjacent to you.",B.r,B.WF,!1)
B.I0=new A.i("feature_guardian_spirits_ancient_sacrifice","Ancient Sacrifice","If the targets of Guardian Spirits or Ancient Conduit would die as a result of the damage, instead set their HP to half. The character cannot be targeted by Guardian Spirits or Ancient Conduit again in this situation.")
B.Mf=new A.i("feature_guardian_spirits_protective_spirits","Protective Spirits","Guardian Spirits grants the target resistance to all damage until the start of their next turn. Ancient Conduit gives the target allies {Source d6} shield.")
