B.P3=new A.a8("feature_hack","Hack","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Int, targeting 1 enemy range {2+Source}. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage and as long as you remain concentrating, the target is hacked and you and your allies have advantage on defenses caused by the target. While concentrating, you may use the target's space as the origin of your abilities that use the same source as hack. While concentrating, if you activate the ability again and succeed, you may add additional targets to your current hacking concentration.\n\n[Reaction] When your ally succeeds on an attack during their turn, you may begin concentrating on hacked targeting one of the targets of the origin attack.",B.r,B.WW,!1)
