B.OQ=new A.a8("feature_hand_of_fate","Hand of Fate","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Cha targeting an enemy range 1. On Success, they take {Half Source d20} damage and the target may not be the target of Hand of Fate again this life. The immunity to Hand of Fate applies regardless of what character uses the feature.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally makes an attack during their turn, spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Cha targeting 1 of the targets of the triggering attack. On Success, deal {Half Source d20} damage. The target may not be targeted by Hand of Fate again.",B.r,B.Uz,!1)
B.N6=new A.i("feature_harm_bully","Bully","Also deal the bonus damage if you are flanking the target or if the origin of the reaction is flanking.")
