B.NB=new A.a8("feature_harm","Harm","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Int targeting an enemy Range 1. On Success, deal {Source d10} damage. If the target is Stunned, Disabled, Restrained, or Prone, deal {Source d6} extra damage.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally succeeds on an attack during their turn, spend your reaction and they deal {Source d6} extra damage to targets that are Stunned, Disabled, Restrained, or Prone.",B.r,B.Uv,!1)
B.Hp=new A.i("feature_haste_all_out","All Out","While concentrating, at the start of the target's turn, they may convert their reaction into an extra action and end the haste effect on themselves at the end of their turn. This doesn't end the effect for other targets.")
B.Jy=new A.i("feature_haste_blurry","Blurry","While concentrating, the target gains advantage on Str and Dex defenses.")
