B.OV=new A.a8("feature_haste","Haste","[Action] Target yourself or an ally range {Source}. While concentrating, gain {Source} bonus speed, and a +1 bonus to results of Str, Dex, and Cha defense results and to attack results that target those defenses. While concentrating, if you activate the power again, you may add targets to the concentration.\n\n[Reaction] During ally turns, spend your reaction and target an ally range 1 and begin concentrating on haste targeting that ally.",B.T,B.VA,!1)
B.II=new A.i("feature_hate_mocking","Mocking","When you use the action, make a ranged attack 6/12 instead, and on success, until the start of your next turn, if the target fails an attack or check, push them {Source}. When you use your reaction, until the triggering character\u2019s next turn, when the target fails an attack or check, push the target {Half Source}.")
B.Jm=new A.i("feature_hate_violent","Violent","With either, until the start of your next turn, when the target fails at attacking they take {Half Source d12} damage.")
