B.Og=new A.a8("feature_hate","Hate","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Int targeting an enemy range 1. On Success, deal {Source d10} damage. Until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on attacks but deals {Source/3 d6} extra damage on success and takes {Source/3 d6} damage on problems.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally succeed on an attack during their turn, spend your reaction and until the start of your next turn, the targets of the triggering attack have disadvantage on attacks but deal {Source/3 d6} extra damage on success and take {Source/3 d6} damage on problems.",B.r,B.X3,!1)
B.JU=new A.i("feature_haunt_right_behind_you","Right Behind You","At the start of a haunted target\u2019s turn, you may teleport to a free space adjacent to the target.")
