B.Ou=new A.a8("feature_haunt","Haunt","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Int targeting an enemy range 1. On Success, they take {Source d10} damage, and until the start of your next turn, you haunt the target. While haunted, if an attack included you as a target, you and your allies resist damage caused by the attack.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally succeeds on an attack during their turn, spend your reaction and target 1 of the targets of the triggering attack. Until the start of the triggering character's next turn, you haunt the target.",B.r,B.VK,!1)
B.HK=new A.i("feature_heal_bodily_regeneration","Bodily Regeneration","On Success with either, the target gains {Half Source d8} Regeneration until the end of their next turn.")
