B.OD=new A.a8("feature_heal","Heal","[Action] Target yourself or an ally range 4 and make a Status Check, and on a Success, heal them equal to {Source d10}. If the target is an ally and range 1, you gain advantage on the check.\n\n[Reaction] During your or an ally turn, spend your reaction, target an ally range 4, and make a Status Check. On Success, heal them {Source d10}. If the target is within 1, you have advantage on the check.",B.T,B.UE,!1)
B.Iy=new A.i("feature_helper_helping_hand_assistant","Assistant","The targets may spend usages of help to reroll skills as long as you are within {Source}.")
