B.Nx=new A.a8("feature_helper_helping_hand","Helper Helping Hand","[Action] Make a status check. On success, target all allies range 1 and give them {Half Source} Help. They may spend 1 help when they spend their [Action] to give any check or attack they make advantage.\n\n[Reaction] During an ally\u2019s turn who is range 1, spend your reaction and give the target {Half Source} Help.\n\n[Reaction] Whenever an ally range 1 is knocked prone, you may spend your reaction and help them up, removing the prone, regardless of body plan.",B.T,B.Uk,!1)
B.IH=new A.i("feature_hexer_rubber_leg_hex","Rubber Leg Hex","While hexed, the target speed is reduced by {Half Source} spaces and they cannot take the [Run] action.")
