B.N9=new A.i("feature_hexer_deaths_hex","Death\u2019s Hex","At the end of a hexed character\u2019s turn, make a Status Check vs Wis. On Success, deal {Half Source d8}.")
B.TY=s([B.IH,B.I7,B.N9],t.U)
B.On=new A.a8("feature_hexer","Hexer","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Wis against 1 enemy range {1+Source}. On Success, deal {Source d10} damage and the target is hexed until the end of your next turn. While hexed, you and your allies have advantage on Status Checks against the target.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally succeeds on an attack during their turn, spend your reaction and all the targets are hexed until the triggering character's next turn. If one of the targets is already hexed, you may end the hex for them to give all the other targets hex without spending your reaction. If your source has costs or effects when using abilities they trigger as normal.",B.r,B.TY,!1)
B.Jb=new A.i("feature_hunter_practiced","Practiced","After using the action, gain {Half Source} rerolls. While concentrating, when you miss with an attack against the target of your Hunt, you may spend 1 reroll to reroll 1 attack dice.")
B.Lc=new A.i("feature_hunter_stalk","Stalk","At the end of your Hunt Target\u2019s turn, you may move {Source} toward the target.")
B.IZ=new A.i("feature_hunter_rending","Rending","While concentrating, [Reaction] When the target takes the [Run] or [Retreat] action and is range 3, spend your reaction and give the target {Half Source} d6 bleed.")
B.Wj=s([B.Jb,B.Lc,B.IZ],t.U)
B.O4=new A.a8("feature_hunter","Hunter","[Action] Target an enemy you can see and begin concentrating on Hunt and make a Conceal check to hide. As long as you are concentrating, all attacks you make against the target deal an extra {Half Source d8} damage and the target cannot target you with opportunity attacks. If you start your turn and your hunt target is dead and you are concentrating on hunt, you may target another creature you can see to be the target of your hunt.\n\n[Reaction] After you or an ally succeed on an attack during their turn, choose 1 of the targets and begin concentration on Hunt and either, dash {Source}, or dash {Half Source} and make a Conceal check to hide yourself.\n\n[Reaction] When you start your turn, you may spend your reaction and target an enemy you can see that becomes the target of your hunt and either dash {Source}, or dash {Half Source} and make a Conceal check to hide yourself, if the target of your hunt has died.",B.r,B.Wj,!1)
B.M5=new A.i("feature_ignite_burning_heat","Burning Heat","When the target takes damage from burns from this ability, each adjacent enemy also takes the damage.")
B.Iw=new A.i("feature_ignite_distracting_flame","Distracting Flame","If a creature starts its turn burning, it has a -1 penalty to all attack results.")
B.LI=new A.i("feature_ignite_pizza_napalm","Pizza Napalm","You may instead make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting an enemy Range 6/12 instead of the Melee Attack. On Success, in addition to the normal effects reduce the target\u2019s speed by {Half Source} while burning.")
B.Wi=s([B.M5,B.Iw,B.LI],t.U)
B.P0=new A.a8("feature_ignite","Ignite","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Vit targeting an enemy range 3. On Success, they take {Source d6} damage and give the target {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Dex. If the target already has burn, instead give its current burn to each enemy adjacent to them then increase its burn by {Half Source d6}.\n\n[Reaction] After you succeed on an attack, spend your reaction. Pick one of the targets of the triggering attack and give the target {Half Source} d6 burn vs Dex. If the target already has burn, instead give its current burn to each enemy adjacent to them then increase its burn by {Half Source d6}.",B.r,B.Wi,!1)
B.Kv=new A.i("feature_illness_contagion","Contagion","When an enemy ends its turn adjacent to an ill character, the enemy gains {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Wis.")
B.Jt=new A.i("feature_illness_ebolize","Ebolize","When a character starts its turn ill, they gain {Source/3} d6 bleed. As long as they have this bleed they are ill.")
B.If=new A.i("feature_illness_vomiting","Vomiting","When a character starts its turn ill, make a Status Check vs Vit. On success, they are disabled and they make 1 of their spaces difficult terrain. On Problems, they are no longer ill and they make 1 space range 1 difficult terrain.")
B.U6=s([B.Kv,B.Jt,B.If],t.U)
B.OZ=new A.a8("feature_illness","Illness","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Vit targeting enemies range 1. On Success, deal {Source d10} damage and they are ill until the start of your next turn. While ill their speed is reduced by {Half Source}.\n\n[Reaction] During your or ally turns, spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Vit. On Success, target all enemies range 1 of the triggering character, and deal {Source d10} and the targets are ill until the start of the triggering character\u2019s next turn.",B.r,B.U6,!1)
B.KM=new A.i("feature_drain_feasting","Feasting","On Success, On the start of your next turn, you may remove up to all your Shield, and heal for twice the amount lost.")
B.I5=new A.i("feature_drain_temptation","Temptation","Regardless of if you succeeded on the action. On the start of your next turn, Make an Status Check vs Wis, On Success, you may Force the target to move {2*Source} space toward you.")
B.Td=s([B.KM,B.I5],t.U)
B.OH=new A.a8("feature_drain","Drain","[Action] Make a Melee Attack Vs Vit targeting an adjacent enemy. On Success, deal {Source d12} damage and gain half the damage as shield.\n\n[Reaction] On Success with a melee attack, gain half the damage as shield. If the trigger targets multiple enemies, only gain it for the damage to 1 of the targets.",B.r,B.Td,!1)
B.LW=new A.i("feature_earthquake_epicenter","Epicenter","Deal {Source d10} damage to enemies range 2 to you instead.")
B.MI=new A.i("feature_earthquake_unstable_earth","Unstable Earth","Reduce all damaged enemies speed by {Half Source} until the end of their next turn.")
B.Jd=new A.i("feature_earthquake_growing_tremors","Growing Tremors","Every time you succeed increase the damage done to all targets by 1d6 to a max of {Power d6}.")
B.Wo=s([B.LW,B.MI,B.Jd],t.U)
B.OJ=new A.a8("feature_earthquake","Earthquake","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack Vs Vit, Targeting Enemies range {1 + Source}. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage. Any targets that are more than {Half Source} spaces away from you take half damage. Resistance applies to this as normal.\n\n[Reaction] End of round, make a Ranged Attack vs Vit targeting enemies range {Source}. On success deal {Source d6} to all targets.",B.r,B.Wo,!1)
B.HL=new A.i("feature_elemental_whip_binding","Binding","On Success, At the start of the target's turn, make an Status Check vs Str, on a Success the target may not move until the start of its next turn.")
B.M3=new A.i("feature_elemental_whip_flinging","Flinging","After pulling the target, push them {Source} Spaces.")
B.K5=new A.i("feature_elemental_whip_swinging","Swinging","Instead of Pulling, you may move to a free space within 3 spaces of the target. Note: You still Fling after Swinging if able.")
B.Vb=s([B.HL,B.M3,B.K5],t.U)
B.Ov=new A.a8("feature_elemental_whip","Elemental Whip","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Dex against 1 enemy Range 3. On Success, deal {Source d12} damage and either knock the target prone or Pull the target adjacent to you.\n\n[Reaction] During Your or an Ally turn, Make a Melee Attack vs Dex against 1 enemy Range 3. On Success: Deal {Source d12} damage and either, Knock the target Prone, or Pull the target Adjacent to you.",B.r,B.Vb,!1)
B.Hi=new A.i("feature_eruption_mud_tunnel","Mud Tunnel","Regardless of if you Succeed on the action or reaction, you may concentrate on eruption, making each space in a line between your start and destination and each space adjacent to the destination difficult terrain for as long as you remain concentrating.")
B.I8=new A.i("feature_eruption_aftershock","Aftershock","At the Start of your next turn, Make a Status Check vs Dex against each Enemy range 1, On Success, Deal {Source d6} damage.")
B.Ia=new A.i("feature_eruption_mountain_maker","Mountain Maker","Until you move from the spot of your eruption, you may not be forced to move or dash and you gain +1 to Defense Results.")
B.X4=s([B.Hi,B.I8,B.Ia],t.U)
B.NJ=new A.a8("feature_eruption","Eruption","[Action] Target a free space within {2 + Source} spaces. You sink into the ground, teleport to that location, then erupt from the ground making a Melee Attack vs Dex against Enemies range 1. On Success, Deal {Source d8} Damage.\n\n[Reaction] Before making a Melee Attack, Spend your reaction and target a free space within {1 + Source} and teleport there. If you succeed on the triggering melee attack deal {Source d8} to each enemy range 1 of you.",B.r,B.X4,!1)
B.KB=new A.i("feature_explosion_after_shock","After Shock","At the start of your next turn after using the action, repeat the attack targeting the same area. Enemies are aware that there will be an aftershock.")
B.MJ=new A.i("feature_explosion_blast","Blast","On Success with either, all enemies targeted are pushed {Source} space away from the center of the radius.")
B.Mr=new A.i("feature_explosion_powerful","Powerful","Increase the attack damage to {Source d10}. Enemies a 1 space radius in the center take {Source d12}.")
B.WR=s([B.KB,B.MJ,B.Mr],t.U)
B.Nn=new A.a8("feature_explosion","Explosion","[Action] Target up to a {Half Source} space radius Range {6 +Half Source}, and make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting enemies there. On Success, they take {Source d8} Damage.\n\n[Reaction] You succeeded on an attack or check using your action that targeted a creature, spend your reaction, Make a Ranged Attack vs Dex targeting a {Half Source} Space radius that contains at least 1 of the targeted creature\u2019s spaces. On Success, deal {Source d8} damage to enemies in the radius.",B.r,B.WR,!1)
B.Hx=new A.i("feature_forced_martyrdom_cruel","Cruel","When you Succeed with the Status Check, Deal {Source d8} Damage to the target.")
B.Lj=new A.i("feature_forced_martyrdom_taunting","Taunting","While the target is affected, they have disadvantage on all attacks that don\u2019t include you as a target.")
B.Hn=new A.i("feature_forced_martyrdom_masochism","Masochism","[Reaction] When you have to make a defense roll, you may spend your reaction to automatically fail the defense roll and the target takes full damage instead of half. You otherwise take half damage and are affected by the attack as normal.")
B.U_=s([B.Hx,B.Lj,B.Hn],t.U)
B.NY=new A.a8("feature_forced_martyrdom","Forced Martyrdom","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Wis targeting an enemy range 1. On Success, Deal {source d8} Damage and you resist all damage from attacks. When you take damage the target takes the same amount. At the start of your turn, make an Status Check vs the target\u2019s Wis, On Success, they continue to be affected, on Miss the effect ends.\n\n[Reaction] After you make an Attack, Make a Status Check vs Wis targeting one of the targets of the triggering attack. On Success, deal {Source d8} damage and you resist all damage from attacks and when you take damage the target takes the same amount. At the start of your turn, make an Status Check vs the target\u2019s Wis, On Success, they continue to be affected, on Problems the effect ends.",B.r,B.U_,!1)
B.Jg=new A.i("feature_illusions_behind_the_curtain","Behind the Curtain","You and your allies can move through your illusions without breaking them. You and your allies may end your turn inside your illusion walls, preventing them from being able to be targeted by enemies as long as there is an illusion. If an enemy would be able to target a creature under your illusion with an ability, they can target the illusions in the spaces instead.")
B.KV=new A.i("feature_illusions_disillusionment","Disillusionment","When an enemy destroys one of your illusions, make a status check vs Int. On success, deal {Source d6} damage to the destroying enemy.")
B.Hj=new A.i("feature_illusions_smoke_and_mirrors","Smoke and Mirrors","When an enemy destroys one of your illusions, you or your allies adjacent to the illusions gain +1 to defense results until the start of their next turn. [Reaction] When you or your allies are adjacent to an illusion and are targeted by an attack, they can spend their reaction to force them to target the illusion instead.")
B.Lu=new A.i("feature_illusions_unnerving_movement","Unnerving Movement","While concentrating, at the start of any turn, spend your [Reaction] target 1 illusion and move it {Source} spaces then make a status check vs Int targeting enemies range {Source} of the illusion. On success, deal {Source d6} damage.")
B.UQ=s([B.Jg,B.KV,B.Hj,B.Lu],t.U)
B.NZ=new A.a8("feature_illusions","Illusions","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Int: On a Success, create up to {Source} spaces worth of illusions that last as long as you remain concentrating. Each space of illusions follows the wall rules from skills. You may create barriers instead of walls, creating 2 spaces of barrier for 1 space of wall. Your illusions are destroyed when hit by a single attack. You and your allies may move through your illusions causing them to be destroyed.\n\n[Reaction] At the start of a turn, spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Int. On Success, create up to {Source} spaces worth of illusions. While concentrating, if you activate the ability, you may add new illusions to the concentration.",B.r,B.UQ,!1)
B.Je=new A.i("feature_inspiration_rage","Rage","When an ally fails on an attack, defense, or skill using inspiration, deal {Source d6} damage targeting an enemy range 1 of them or you.")
B.J6=new A.i("feature_inspiration_hope","Hope","When an ally succeeds on a defense using inspiration, give you and your allies {Half Source d6} shield.")
B.Kx=new A.i("feature_inspiration_valor","Valor","Once each round, after you are damaged by an attack, each of your allies with inspiration gains {Source/3 d6} shield.")
B.UM=s([B.Je,B.J6,B.Kx],t.U)
B.O6=new A.a8("feature_inspiration","Inspiration","Inspire [Reaction]: After you or an ally you see succeeds on a check or attack during their turn, target {Source} allies and give them an Inspiration. When they would make an attack, defense, or skill roll, they may spend the inspiration to gain advantage. All inspiration is lost at the end of the situation.\n\nInspiring Valor [Action]: Make either a Melee Attack vs Str range 1 or a Ranged Attack vs Dex range 4. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage to an enemy in range and all allies range {Source} gain shield equal to half the damage you deal.",B.T,B.UM,!1)
B.KX=new A.i("feature_jinx_doom","Doom","While concentrating, at the end of the round, spend your [Reaction] make a Ranged Attack vs Cha. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage to each enemy affected by your jinx.")
B.Ic=new A.i("feature_jinx_confusion","Confusion","You and your allies gain a +1 to defense results caused by jinxed enemies.")
B.Id=new A.i("feature_jinx_sleepy","Sleepy","Jinxed enemies reduce their speed by {Half Source} and cannot use the [Retreat] action.")
B.Ug=s([B.KX,B.Ic,B.Id],t.U)
B.NW=new A.a8("feature_jinx","Jinx","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Cha targeting each enemy range {1+Source}. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage and as long as you remain concentrating, Jinx the targets. While Jinxed, you and all your allies have advantage on attacks against the targets.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally succeeds on an attack during their turn, spend your reaction and all the targets of the origin attack take {Half Source d6} and are jinxed as long as you are concentrating. While concentrating, if you activate the power again, you may add the targeted enemies to the group you are concentrating on.",B.r,B.Ug,!1)
B.MV=new A.i("feature_justice_holy_fire","Holy Fire","Enemies damaged by justice also gain {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Cha.")
B.Hl=new A.i("feature_justice_smiting","Smiting","Instead of targeting an enemy range 1 for damage with the action, choose 1 enemy in the situation.")
B.IN=new A.i("feature_justice_overprotective","Overprotective","For Each HP of healing beyond the targets max hp, grant them 1 Shield up to {2 * Source}. This shield doesn\u2019t cause extra damage, unless you also deal the extra damage to yourself.")
B.Ue=s([B.MV,B.Hl,B.IN],t.U)
B.Ob=new A.a8("feature_justice","Justice","'[Action] Target an ally range 3 and make a Status Check vs Cha, On Success: Heal the target {Source d6}, and target an enemy range 1 from that ally and deal damage equal to the amount the ally was healed. Allies may not be healed over their max HP. Enemies are only damaged by the amount of HP the ally regains. This ability may deal 0 damage.\n\n[Reaction] After you or an ally fails a defense, spend your reaction, make a Status Check vs Cha, On Success, deal {Source d6} damage to the attacking enemy and heal the target by half as much. This happens after the attack is completed. ",B.T,B.Ue,!1)
B.Kh=new A.i("lay_on_hands_righteous","Righteous","Until the end of your next turn, you deal extra damage on all attacks equal to the amount of HP you lost when using Lay on Hands.")
B.I3=new A.i("lay_on_hands_sacrifice","Sacrifice","You may concentrate on your Lay on Hands. As long as you do, at the end of your turn, lose {Source} HP and the target gains {2 * Source} HP. If this damage would cause you to die, the target regains all their health.")
B.Ll=new A.i("lay_on_hands_witness","Witness","All allies not targeted that can see you use Lay on Hands gain shield equal to the HP you lost.")
B.UF=s([B.Kh,B.I3,B.Ll],t.U)
B.No=new A.a8("lay_on_hands","Lay on Hands","[Action]: Target an Ally within range 1. You may lose HP up to {2 * Source}, and heal the target for twice that amount. Targeted Ally also gains {Source d12} Shield if you lose at least {Source} HP.\n\n[Reaction]: During ally turns when the ally is within range 1, spend your reaction and trigger your Lay on Hands.",B.T,B.UF,!1)
B.ME=new A.i("feature_lightning_charger","Charger","You may target yourself or allies with the repeat attack. Instead of damage, give them {Source d6} shield. You may not target yourself or any ally more than once. When you use your reaction, you and allies adjacent to any of the targets gain {Half Source d6} shield.")
B.HW=new A.i("feature_lightning_growing_static","Growing Static","On success with the action, give the last target in the chain 1d6 Burn vs Vit for every {6 - Power} enemies targeted.")
B.Hs=new A.i("feature_lightning_grounded","Grounded","Targets cannot stand from prone until the start of your next turn.")
B.X8=s([B.ME,B.HW,B.Hs],t.U)
B.O7=new A.a8("feature_lightning","Lightning","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Dex targeting an enemy range 3. On success, target another enemy range 3 of that enemy. Repeat targeting enemies range 3 of the last target, never targeting an enemy more than once until out of targets. Deal {Source d6} damage to all targets and knock the targets prone.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally range 3 succeed on an Attack during their turn, Spend your reaction and target all of the targets of the triggering attack, deal {Half Source d6} + 1d6 for each enemy targeted beyond the first and knock them prone.",B.r,B.X8,!1)
B.K8=new A.i("feature_mind_control_battered_mind","Battered Mind","On success, deal {source d8} damage to the target.")
B.Il=new A.i("feature_mind_control_pion","Pion","while concentrating, [Reaction] if an attack would target you and the target is within {Half Source} of you, Spend your reaction and have the attack target the target instead. Then make a concentrating check as if you had taken damage.")
B.M8=new A.i("feature_mind_control_traitor","Traitor","the target has advantage on attacks against their allies.")
B.WI=s([B.K8,B.Il,B.M8],t.U)
B.Ns=new A.a8("feature_mind_control","Mind Control","[Action] make a Ranged Attack vs Int against 1 enemy range {Source}. On success, for as long as you remain concentrating you are disabled and the target is mind controlled. At the start of their turn, make a status check vs Int, on success you control them on their turn. On failure the enemy is disabled this turn and the effect ends. \n\n[Reaction] When you or an Ally Succeed on an Attack during their turn, Spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Int. On Success, 1 of the targets is mind controlled as long as you concentrate.\n",B.r,B.WI,!1)
B.K0=new A.i("feature_minkisi_witch_doctor","Witch Doctor","While concentrating, During your turn [Reaction] if the target is under a status effect that requires an ongoing check, have the target immediately make the check with advantage. The target may instead end burn or bleed. If the target is targeted by a poppet ability, the source of the poppet must make a concentration check.")
B.J_=new A.i("feature_minkisi_witch_trap","Witch Trap","While concentrating, [reaction] when the target fails an Int, Wis, or Cha defense from an attack, you may spend your reaction to have the attacker become the target of the attack instead of the target, suffering the damage and adverse effects from the attack. ")
B.JW=new A.i("feature_minkisi_zombie","Zombie","While concentrating, the target gains resistance to damage that targets Int, Wis or Cha.")
B.Ux=s([B.K0,B.J_,B.JW],t.U)
B.NI=new A.a8("feature_minkisi","Minkisi","[Action]: Target an ally in the initiative and make a status check. On success, make a minkisi that lasts as long as you remain concentrating. When you succeed, heal the target {Source d6} HP. The minkisi requires a hand to carry. Whenever you end your turn holding the minkisi, heal the target {Half Source d6}. \n\n[Reaction] During Ally turns, when they are range 1. Spend your reaction and take the minkisi action targeting the ally.\n\n[Reaction] While concentrating on a minkisi, during the target\u2019s turn, Spend your reaction and choose an ally within {Half Source} of the minkisi target and make a Status check. On Success heal the chosen ally {Source d6}.\n",B.T,B.Ux,!1)
B.IC=new A.i("feature_mirror_blurring","Blurring","while concentrating, After a clone is broken, you gain a +1 to defense results until the start of your next turn.")
B.Lm=new A.i("feature_mirror_phantom_attacks","Phantom Attacks","when you succeed on an attack, deal 1d6 extra damage for each mirror that would also be able to target the target with the same attack.")
B.MH=new A.i("feature_mirror_self_Shattering","Shattering","when one of your mirrors is destroyed, Deal the damage to each enemy range {Source} of the clone. Deal the reaction damage to enemies Range {source} of you.")
B.Ud=s([B.IC,B.Lm,B.MH],t.U)
B.Nk=new A.a8("feature_mirror_self","Mirror Self","[Action] Make {Source} copies of yourself that appear adjacent to you and last for as long as you remain concentrating. Whenever an attack targets you or a clone, you may choose to make a defense like normal or have the clone break. If broken, the clone is destroyed and the attack is otherwise ignored and the attacker takes {Half Source d6} damage. At the start of your turn, pick any of the copies to play out your turn from and you may move all your clones up to your speed whenever you move. Clones damaged from provoked attacks on your turn are destroyed instead of rolling to see who is hit, dealing {Half Source d6} damage to the attacker. If an attack targets multiple of your clones you can only defend for 1 of them.\n\n[Reaction] Before you make a defense check that isn\u2019t a Vitality Defense, Spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Int. On Success, You succeed the check and the attacker takes {Source d6}, On Problems you fail the defense.\n",B.T,B.Ud,!1)
B.L5=new A.i("feature_mischief_Cuteify","Cuteify","On Success with the action, on the start of target\u2019s turn make a status check vs cha, on success the target is disabled and the effect continues. On failure the effect ends.")
B.JD=new A.i("feature_mischief_Glitter_Bomb","Glitter Bomb","Deal damage after moving the target and deal the damage to each enemy within 2 of the target.")
B.Mo=new A.i("feature_mischief_Pants","Pants","On success, the target's speed is halved until they spend a [Reaction] to put their clothes right.")
B.UH=s([B.L5,B.JD,B.Mo],t.U)
B.OU=new A.a8("feature_mischief","Mischief","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack against one enemy in range 6/12 vs Cha. On Success, they take {Source d8} Damage and you may force them to move {Source} spaces.\n\n[Reaction] End of an enemy\u2019s turn who is range 6, Spend your reaction and make a Ranged Attack vs Cha targeting that enemy. On Success, Deal {Source d8} damage and force them to move up to {Source} spaces.\n",B.r,B.UH,!1)
B.I6=new A.i("feature_missile_barrage_Big_One","Big One","The first missile deals {Half source d6} extra damage.")
B.Ip=new A.i("feature_missile_barrage_Explosive","Explosive","You may force targets to dash 1 space per missile. You may target yourself or allies range 6, they resist the damage and are forced to dash {Half Source} spaces per missile instead.")
B.KY=new A.i("feature_missile_barrage_Tracking","Tracking","On problems with the Action, You gain half of the missiles you would have had as tracking missiles that last until the end of your next turn. If you succeed on an attack or take the Missile reaction, you may distribute these tracking missiles to the targets to deal 1d6 damage. These missiles don\u2019t trigger the Big one.")
B.TG=s([B.I6,B.Ip,B.KY],t.U)
B.P_=new A.a8("feature_missile_barrage","Missile Barrage","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs dex, On Success, Distribute {1 + Source} missiles between targets Range 6. Each target takes 1d6 Damage per missile.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an Ally succeed on an Attack during their turn, Spend your reaction and Distribute {1 + Half Source} Missiles between the targets of the triggering attack. Each target takes 1d6 damage per missile.\n",B.r,B.TG,!1)
B.JX=new A.i("feature_mortar_Boom","Boom","On Success, Deal {source d12} damage to targets who are not prone instead. Targets may choose to drop prone before being attacked.")
B.Hu=new A.i("feature_mortar_Scooting","Scooting","During your turn, you may dash your mortar to a free space within {Source} of it.")
B.M1=new A.i("feature_mortar_Relay","Relay","[Reaction] Before an Ally makes an attack, you may spend your reaction and have them use a space within {Source} of your mortar as the origin of the ability and gain a +1 to attack results for that ability.")
B.TF=s([B.JX,B.Hu,B.M1],t.U)
B.OA=new A.a8("feature_mortar","Mortar","[Action] During your or an Ally\u2019s Turns, Spend your reaction and Target a free space range 1 and setup and fire your Mortar. Your mortar counts as a Barrier as if made by a skill, and you may spend supply to do anything but make multiple mortars as if it was a barrier. As long as it lasts, You and your allies can spend a [Reaction] to target a 1 space radius range {Source *3} of the mortar, they make a Ranged Attack vs Dex, and on success deal {Source d8} damage.\n\nFollow up: [Reaction] When an ally range {2*Source} of your Mortar Succeeds on an attack during their turn, Spend your reaction and make a Ranged Attack vs Dex, On Success deal {Source d8} to enemies in a 1 space radius that contains at least 1 space containing a target of the triggering attack. ",B.r,B.TF,!1)
B.Jj=new A.i("feature_mushrooms_Skippers","Skippers","For Enemies, On success Reduce their speed by {Half Source}. For Allies, On Success, Give them {Half Source} additional speed until the start of your turn. You may move your Mushrooms up to {Half Source} Spaces during each of your turns.")
B.J0=new A.i("feature_mushrooms_Stoners","Stoners","For Enemies, On Success: The enemy is stunned until the end of its turn but may not be stunned by stoners again this encounter. For Allies, On Success, The target has advantage on Int, Wis, and Cha defenses and disadvantage on concentration checks until the start of their next turn.")
B.HR=new A.i("feature_mushrooms_Creepers","Creepers","while concentrating, [Action] make the status check targeting every creature range 1 of the area.")
B.Tk=s([B.Jj,B.J0,B.HR],t.U)
B.Nv=new A.a8("feature_mushrooms","Mushrooms","[Action] Target a 1 space radius range 6 spaces, where mushrooms sprout from the ground. For as long as you remain concentrating, Whenever a creature starts their turn in the area or enters it for the first time on their turn, the mushrooms activate. For enemies, make a Status Check Vs Vit, On a Success, deal {Source d6} Damage. For Allies, make a Status Check, On Success, Heal {Source d6} HP.\n\nSpores [Reaction] During your or ally turns, Spend your action, and make a Status Check vs Vit. On Success, target all characters range 1 of the Triggering Character, Deal {Source d6} to Enemies and Heal {Source d6} to allies.\n",B.r,B.Tk,!1)
B.LX=new A.i("feature_nightmare_Scream","Scream","When you fail the status check on a character with nightmares, make a status check vs cha targeting enemies within {Source} of the original target, excluding the original target. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage.")
B.M2=new A.i("feature_nightmare_Monsters_Under_the_Bed","Monsters Under the Bed","When you succeed on the status check, deal 1d10 extra damage for each of your allies adjacent to the target.")
B.IB=new A.i("feature_nightmare_Crawling","Crawling","when you succeed on the status check, force the target to move {Half Source} ignoring the prone during the movement.")
B.Ur=s([B.LX,B.M2,B.IB],t.U)
B.O_=new A.a8("feature_nightmare","Nightmare","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Int targeting 1 enemy range 4. On success, the target is knocked prone and is trapped in nightmares and is stunned. While having nightmares, on the start of the target's turn, make a status check vs int, on success the target is stunned and takes {Source d8} damage. On failure the effect ends. If the target is attacked by you or your allies, the effect ends.\n\n[Reaction] Start of an enemy turn who is range 4 of you and has you or one of your allies adjacent to it. Make a Ranged Attack vs Int. On success, the target is knocked prone, is stunned and has nightmares.\n",B.r,B.Ur,!1)
B.HG=new A.i("feature_ninja_Shuriken","Shuriken","Before Disappear or Withdraw, make an Ranged Attack targeting 1 enemy range 3/6 vs dex, On Success, Deal {Source d8} Damage.")
B.MA=new A.i("feature_ninja_Shadow_Blade","Shadow Blade","After you Disappear or Withdraw, your next Melee Attack deals an extra {Half Source d8} damage.")
B.Js=new A.i("feature_ninja_Return","Return","Before Disappearing or Withdrawing, target 1 enemy range 1. During your next turn, you may teleport to a free space adjacent to the targeted enemy one time.")
B.VB=s([B.HG,B.MA,B.Js],t.U)
B.OS=new A.a8("feature_ninja","Ninja","Disappear: [Reaction] Start of any turn, Spend your reaction, Dash {Source} spaces to a free space then make a Conceal check to hide.\n\nWithdraw [Reaction] After you or an Ally makes an Attack during their turn, Spend your reaction, Dash {Half Source} Spaces to a free space then make a Conceal check to Hide.\n",B.T,B.VB,!1)
B.Mu=new A.i("feature_ooze_Acidic","Acidic","[Reaction] When damaged by an attack while concentrating on ooze, spend your reaction to Make an Status Check Vs Vit and target absorbed enemies and adjacent enemies. On a Success deal {Source d6} damage. If you fail to concentrate, this effect still occurs.")
B.Jo=new A.i("feature_ooze_First_Hunter","First Hunter","You have advantage on concentration checks caused by targets, and +1 to defense results from attacks made by the targets.")
B.Mw=new A.i("feature_ooze_Amoeba","Amoeba","While Concentrating, You cannot be flanked, and you suffer no speed penalty for squeezing. At the start of your turn, you and the targets all dash {Half Source} spaces to free spaces where you can all fit and the targets are still all range 1 of you.")
B.Vc=s([B.Mu,B.Jo,B.Mw],t.U)
B.Of=new A.a8("feature_ooze","Ooze","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting enemies range 1. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage to each target and absorb the targets as long as you remain concentrating. While absorbed you and the targets are restrained, and at the start of your turn, Deal {Half Source d6} damage to each target and heal {Half Source d6}. You have a +1 to concentration check results caused by the targets.\n\n[Reaction] When an enemy starts or becomes range 1, Spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting the enemy. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage and absorb the target as long as you remain concentrating.\n",B.r,B.Vc,!1)
B.Jq=new A.i("feature_parry_Duelers_Dance","Dueler\u2019s Dance","On Success with your parry, You may move up to {Source} Spaces without provoking attacks. Then force the target into a free space adjacent to you.")
B.Ln=new A.i("feature_parry_Protecting","Protecting","When an Ally is attacked by an enemy who is in range, you may parry the attack. On a miss, the ally still makes a defense against the attack.")
B.Wt=s([B.Jq,B.Ln],t.U)
B.P2=new A.a8("feature_parry","Parry","Parry [Reaction] If an enemy range 1 would attack you, You may spend your reaction to make an Attack roll. On Success, Deal {Source d10} damage and the Enemy attack misses. On a miss, the attack succeeds against you. You may use a weapon instead targeting within the weapons reach, and dealing the weapon\u2019s damage ignoring the weapon\u2019s technique.\n\nPrepare [Action] until the start of your next turn, you may parry {source} times without spending your reaction\n",B.r,B.Wt,!1)
B.LA=new A.i("feature_pin_Executioner","Executioner","When allies hit your pin target, they deal {Half Source d6} extra damage.")
B.Na=new A.i("feature_pin_Guard_Master","Guard Master","At the end of a grappled enemies adjacent to you turn, instead of them moving in the grapple, you may move them in the grapple instead. ")
B.IE=new A.i("feature_pin_Limb_Lock","Limb Lock","While Pinning, Enemies adjacent to you have disadvantage on attacks against you and to escape grapple. You have disadvantage on attacks against the targets of your Pinning.")
B.Tb=s([B.LA,B.Na,B.IE],t.U)
B.NN=new A.a8("feature_pin","Pin","Pin [Action, 2 Unarmed] Make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting an enemy within 1. On Success, deal {Source d6} and you grapple the target and have pinning as long as you remain grappling. While Pinning, enemies adjacent to you grant your allies advantage when making Attacks from outside the grapple against the target rather than disadvantage. If they roll 2 failures they attack you instead. \n\n[Reaction] When an enemy starts its turn adjacent to you or becomes adjacent, Spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack vs Str. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage and grapple the target and gain pinning as long as you remain grappling.\n",B.r,B.Tb,!1)
B.IQ=new A.i("feature_poppet_Eyes","Eyes","While concentrating, During your turn you may spend your [Reaction] until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on ranged attacks and defense checks caused by attacks from non adjacent attackers.")
B.Kq=new A.i("feature_poppet_Heart","Heart","While concentrating, During your turn you may spend your [Reaction] deal {Half Source d6} damage ignoring shield and resistance. ")
B.LB=new A.i("feature_poppet_Junk","Junk","While concentrating, During your turn you may spend your [Reaction] the target must make a concentration check with disadvantage if concentrating. Until the start of your next turn, reduce the target's speed by {Source} to no less than 1.")
B.Vs=s([B.IQ,B.Kq,B.LB],t.U)
B.Ng=new A.a8("feature_poppet","Poppet","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Cha targeting 1 enemy range 1. On Success, deal {Source d8} damage and you make a poppet of the target that lasts as long as you remain concentrating. While concentrating, you and your allies have a +1 to attack results against the target and +1 to defense results caused by the target. The poppet requires a hand to wield.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally succeeds with a melee attack during their turn and has a free hand, spend your reaction and create a poppet for 1 of the targets. If an ally is the triggering character, you still concentrate on the poppet even when they are holding it. \n",B.r,B.Vs,!1)
B.KJ=new A.i("feature_puppet_Guilt","Guilt","When your puppet succeeds in attacking one of their allies, The puppet takes {Source d8} Damage.")
B.Kf=new A.i("feature_puppet_BodyGuard","BodyGuard","[Reaction] When an attack would target you, you may spend your reaction to teleport your puppet to a free space adjacent to you and it becomes the target of the attack instead.")
B.Jk=new A.i("feature_puppet_Distant_Strings","Distant Strings","The attack becomes Ranged with a range becomes {2*Source} /{4*Source}. If you Succeed on an attack at the long range, you have advantage on your first {Source} Status Checks vs the Target.")
B.Wg=s([B.KJ,B.Kf,B.Jk],t.U)
B.Or=new A.a8("feature_puppet","Puppet","[Action] Melee Attack vs Int targeting 1 enemy range {Source}, On Success: The target is your puppet as long as you remain concentrating. On the Start of Its Turn, Make an Status Check Vs Int, On Success: You may have the target move up to its speed and use a single Innate Action, [Chump Action], or Skill in combat action against a target of your choice. On a Miss: The target is stunned and the effect ends.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally Succeeds on an Attack during their turn, Spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Int, On Success the target becomes your puppet for as long as you remain concentrating.\n",B.r,B.Wg,!1)
B.MR=new A.i("feature_rain_Ice_Storm","Ice Storm","On Success, Give targeted enemies {Source /3} cold. While Concentrating, At the start of your Turn, Make an Status Check vs Wis, On Success, enemies in the area gain {Source /3} cold.")
B.KO=new A.i("feature_rain_Wandering_Storm","Wandering Storm","While Concentrating, At the Start of the Round, you may move your rain area {Source} Spaces.")
B.MG=new A.i("feature_rain_Soothing_Rain","Soothing Rain","when an ally ends their turn in the area they gain {Source d6} shield. This includes the bonus to gaining shields in the area.")
B.VD=s([B.MR,B.KO,B.MG],t.U)
B.OO=new A.a8("feature_rain","Rain","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Wis, targeting enemies in a 1 space radius range 6. On Success, they take {Source d8} Damage. Regardless, the area remains under a rain cloud as long as you remain concentrating. Whenever an enemy in the area is attacked, they take an extra {half Source d6} damage. Whenever an ally in the area gains shield or heals, increase the amount by {Half Source d6}.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally succeeds on an Attack during their turn, spend your reaction and place a 1 space radius rain cloud so that at least 1 of the spaces of a target of the triggering attack is in the radius that lasts as long as you remain concentrating. Apply the bonus damage to the triggering attack.\n",B.r,B.VD,!1)
B.L3=new A.i("feature_rally_Boastful","Boastful","On Success, you gain either the healing or the bonus, your choice on each use. If you have mobilizing, you may gain that speed instead of the other options.")
B.Ho=new A.i("feature_rally_Protective","Protective","For Each HP of healing beyond the targets max hp, grant them 1 Shield up to {2 * Source}.")
B.Jn=new A.i("feature_rally_Mobilizing","Mobilizing","On Success with the action, all targeted allies may move {Source} without provoking attacks. On success with the reaction, the triggering ally may move {Source} without provoking attack.")
B.UR=s([B.L3,B.Ho,B.Jn],t.U)
B.NX=new A.a8("feature_rally","Rally","[Action] make a status check, on success, target all allies range 4 and heal them {Source d6} and they gain +1 to the results of either attacks or defenses until the start of your next turn. Pick which bonus each time you use the ability.\n\n[Reaction] After an Ally takes damage from an attack, Spend your reaction and make a status check, On Success, target the triggering ally and all allies range 4 and heal them {Source d6} and they gain +1 to the results of either attacks or defenses until the start of your next turn. Pick which bonus each time you use the ability.\n",B.T,B.UR,!1)
B.HX=new A.i("feature_rot_Festering","Festering","When Rot prevents Healing or Shield the target takes Damage equal to what they would have gained.")
B.HH=new A.i("feature_rot_Parasitic","Parasitic","When Rot prevents Healing or Shield, you gain that Healing or Shield instead. You have advantage on Concentration Checks caused by the Target.")
B.Lg=new A.i("feature_rot_Plague ","Plague","[Reaction] While Concentrating, Whenever an Enemy Range {Source} of the target would heal or Gain Shield, you may Spend your Reaction to prevent them from healing or gaining shield.")
B.W0=s([B.HX,B.HH,B.Lg],t.U)
B.OF=new A.a8("feature_rot","Rot","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack Vs Vit targeting an enemy range 6/12: On Success, deal {Source d8} damage and begin concentrating. As long as you remain concentrating, When the target would gain HP or Shield they do not. While Concentrating, If you use this ability again, you may add targets to the concentration.\n\n[Reaction] When an enemy range 6 would heal or gain shield, Spend your reaction and make a Ranged Attack vs Vit. On success, the target doesn\u2019t heal or gain shield and takes {Source d6} damage.\n",B.r,B.W0,!1)
B.Md=new A.i("feature_rupture_Dripping","Dripping","The spaces adjacent to ruptured enemies is difficult terrain for enemies. After ruptured enemies take bleed damage and do not move enough to trigger rupture, make a Status Check vs Dex. On Success, they fall prone.")
B.JT=new A.i("feature_rupture_Ripping","Ripping","On Success with the Action or Reaction, Deal {Half Source d12} to the targets if they already have bleed.")
B.JQ=new A.i("feature_rupture_BloodWalker","BloodWalker","Once during your turn, when adjacent to a Creature with Bleed you may teleport to a space adjacent to a creature with Bleed.")
B.Uf=s([B.Md,B.JT,B.JQ],t.U)
B.OL=new A.a8("feature_rupture","Rupture","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Vit targeting an enemy range 1. On Success, give the target {Source} d6 Rupture Bleed. As long as they have Rupture Bleed, before rolling the bleed, if they moved or dashed more than 1 space this turn, increase the dice size of the bleed by 2 to a max of d12. \n\n[Reaction] When you Succeed on an Attack, Spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Vit. On Success, give all the targets of the triggering attack, {Source} d6 Rupture Bleed.\n",B.r,B.Uf,!1)
B.JS=new A.i("feature_sanctuary_Sleepy","Sleepy","When allies gain rest, If they are prone or choose to drop prone, they gain both benefits. When an ally in the sanctuary benefits from the extra healing or shield, they may drop prone to gain {Source d6} extra instead.")
B.LY=new A.i("feature_sanctuary_Guardian","Guardian","[Reaction] When an enemy starts its turn in your sanctuary or enters for the first time, Make a Melee Attack vs Wis. On Success, Deal {Source d6} damage and the target is restrained until the end of its turn. Regardless, dash to a free space adjacent to the target.")
B.Jp=new A.i("feature_sanctuary_Orchard","Orchard","Your allies may spend their [Reaction] During their turn when they are in the sanctuary and there are no adjacent enemies to heal {Half Source d6} and gain {Half Source d6} shield. Note: this doesn\u2019t trigger sanctuary.")
B.JP=new A.i("feature_sanctuary_Hallowed","Hallowed","All Creatures in the sanctuary have +1 to defense results. Whenever a creature in the sanctuary deals damage, they take {Source/3 d6} damage. If you have Guardian, you do not have to make concentration checks because of this damage.")
B.UU=s([B.JS,B.LY,B.Jp,B.JP],t.U)
B.Nz=new A.a8("feature_sanctuary","Sanctuary","Sanctuary [Action] Create a sanctuary that is a {Source} radius area containing at least 1 of your spaces for as long as you remain concentrating. While concentrating, when an ally in the sanctuary is healed or given shield by an ability other than this ability, they gain {Half Source d6} extra healing or shield. If an effect grants both, they choose either a bonus to healing or shield. Healing from regenerating in the area also gains this bonus healing. If an ability has multiple healing or shielding effects, only grant the bonus once per target.\n\nRest [Reaction] During your or ally turns, Spend your reaction and make a Status Check. On Success you and all your allies in the Sanctuary may either Heal {Half Source d6} or gain {Half Source d6} shield, decided by each character. If they do not have an enemy adjacent to them, they gain {Source d6} instead.\n",B.T,B.UU,!1)
B.KZ=new A.i("feature_size_change_Apex","Apex","Grow: Gain +1 Range, when you target creatures smaller than you, gain a +1 to attack and check results. Shrink: gain a +1 to defenses caused by creatures larger than you and you don't provoke attacks.")
B.HM=new A.i("feature_size_change_everchanging_size","EverChanging Size","If you have Grow, gain Shrink. If you have Shrink, gain Grow. At the start of your turn you may switch between shrink or grow.")
B.JO=new A.i("feature_size_change_gift_of_change","Gift of Change","You may target an ally within 3 instead. You may not give the target a size perk they already have.")
B.V7=s([B.KZ,B.HM,B.JO],t.U)
B.NC=new A.a8("feature_size_change","Size Change","Shrink/Grow [Reaction] During your turn spend your reaction. For as long as you are concentrating, Grow or Shrink in size. While Growing, increase your size by 1 and pick a size perk for the new size you have gained. If you were already large, gain another large perk. While Shrinking, decrease your size by 1 and pick a size perk for your new size. If you were already small, pick another small perk. Use {source} instead of level in any calculations.",B.T,B.V7,!1)
B.J1=new A.i("feature_shadow_dancer_Lead_your_Partner","Lead Your Partner","When you shadow dance, You may bring 1 adjacent ally with you and teleport them to an unoccupied square adjacent to your new location. They may not be teleported above another creature. The Ally gains Shadow\u2019s Edge & Shadow\u2019s Grace if Available.")
B.Ib=new A.i("feature_shadow_dancer_Shadow_Edge","Shadow\u2019s Edge","After you use Shadow Dance, Your next Attack deals an extra {Half Source d8} Damage.")
B.Hq=new A.i("feature_shadow_dancer_Shadow_Grace","Shadow\u2019s Grace","After you use Shadow Dance, Gain {Source} speed and your movement doesn\u2019t provoke attacks of opportunity until the end of your next turn.")
B.VJ=s([B.J1,B.Ib,B.Hq],t.U)
B.NT=new A.a8("feature_shadow_dancer","Shadow Dancer","Shadow Dance [Reaction] During your turn, If you are within 1 space of a creature, spend your reaction and you may teleport up to {2* Source}, to a Free Space adjacent to a creature. You may not teleport above a creature.\n\n[Reaction] End of any Turn if there is a character within 1 of you, spend your reaction and teleport up to {2* Source} to a free space adjacent to a creature. You may not Teleport above a creature.\n",B.T,B.VJ,!1)
B.HZ=new A.i("feature_snuff_out_area","Area","On success, deal the damage and extra burn damage to all enemies range {Half Source} of the target.")
B.Mc=new A.i("feature_snuff_out_ember","Ember","On Success, Until the end of your next turn, the first time the target would gain Burn, They gain {Half Source} extra d6 Burn vs Dex. ")
B.LG=new A.i("feature_snuff_out_smoke","Smoke","On Success, until the start of the targets turn, the target and enemies within {Source} of the target have a -1 to attack results.")
B.Is=new A.i("feature_snuff_out_murderous_glee","Murderous Glee","Whenever you kill a target with snuff out, gain {Source d12} shield, and dash to a free space within {Source}. Until the end of your next turn or for as long as you concentrate, you and your allies have advantage on attacks against targets within {Source} spaces of you.")
B.VN=s([B.HZ,B.Mc,B.LG,B.Is],t.U)
B.NA=new A.a8("feature_snuff_out","Snuff Out","[Action] make a melee attack vs Dex targeting 1 enemy range 5 with burn. On Success, deal {Source d8}, and have the target roll and take their burn damage then end their burn. \n\n[Reaction] When an enemy range 3 rolls burn dice, Spend your Reaction and make a status Check vs the same defense as the burn. On Success, the target rolls their burn again and also takes {Source d6}, Then end the burn.\n",B.r,B.VN,!1)
B.JM=new A.i("feature_slap_duel","Duel","On success, pick one of the targets, until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on attacks that don't include you as a target and you have disadvantage on attacks that don\u2019t include the target as a target.")
B.Mb=new A.i("feature_slap_how_dare_you","How Dare You","On Success, Until the end of your next turn, after the target attacks you, deal {Half Source d6} damage to the enemy regardless of success.")
B.JE=new A.i("feature_slap_shame","Shame","On Success, You and your allies gain a +1 to on defense results from the target's attacks until the start of your next turn. ")
B.US=s([B.JM,B.Mb,B.JE],t.U)
B.Os=new A.a8("feature_slap","Slap","[Action] Make a Melee Attack Vs Vit targeting each enemy within 1. On Success, deal {Source d12} damage and the targets may not make attacks of opportunity until the start of your next turn. \n\n[Reaction] Before an enemy range 1 makes an opportunity attack, make a Melee Attack vs Vit. On success, deal {Source d12} damage and the opportunity attack misses. \n",B.r,B.US,!1)
B.Ne=new A.i("feature_sleep_dream_thief","Dream Thief","On succeeding the status check, Gain {Source d6} shields and the target loses the same amount of shield if they have any. If they have no shield, you may have them take damage instead, ending the effect.")
B.Kz=new A.i("feature_sleep_dream_walker","Dream Walker","Once during your turn, you may teleport to a space adjacent to a sleeping character. When you and your allies move, they may teleport from a space adjacent to a sleeping target to another space adjacent to a sleeping target.")
B.MM=new A.i("feature_sleep_exhaustion","Exhaustion","When the effect ends, the target\u2019s speed is reduced by {Half Source} until the end of their turn. ")
B.WY=s([B.Ne,B.Kz,B.MM],t.U)
B.NU=new A.a8("feature_sleep","Sleep","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Cha. On success target up to {Source} enemies range 6, and knock them prone and asleep. On the start of their turn, make a status check vs Wis. On success, they are stunned and remain asleep. Otherwise the effect ends for the target and they take their turn as normal. When sleeping, if an enemy is attacked or takes damage they wake up and the effect ends. An ally can spend an [Action] or [Reaction] to wake an ally.\n\n[Reaction] when an enemy is knocked prone, spend your reaction and make a status check vs Cha. On success, put the target and all prone enemies to sleep. If it is the target's turn, immediately make the status check as if it was the start of their turn. \n",B.r,B.WY,!1)
B.ID=new A.i("feature_silence_voice_thief","Voice Thief","While Concentrating, Enemies range {Source} of you who are allies with one of the targets are creeped out by you using their voice. While in range, you and your allies gain a +1 to Int, Wis, Cha attack results against those enemies and +1 to Int, Wis, Cha Defense results from attacks caused by the enemies.")
B.JL=new A.i("feature_silence_sore_throat","Sore Throat","While concentrating, At the Start of your turn, gain 1d6 Sore Throat dice then roll your sore throat dice dealing that much damage to all targets. You may gain a max of {Source} sore throat dice.")
B.Ky=new A.i("feature_silence_frustrating","Frustrating","While concentrating, Targets get a -1 to all skill and attack checks that do not include you as a target.")
B.Xb=s([B.ID,B.JL,B.Ky],t.U)
B.Oe=new A.a8("feature_silence","Silence","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Int targeting Enemies in a {Half Source} space radius range 6/12. On Success, the targets are Silenced for as long as you remain concentrating. While silenced, they may not activate combat features, but can otherwise take their turn. If player characters gain this effect they cannot speak and must mime. If playing over voice only, they may only make noises. Chumps cannot trigger their chump actions.\n\n[Reaction] when you succeed on an attack, spend your reaction and start concentrating on silence targeting the triggering attack\u2019s targets. \n",B.r,B.Xb,!1)
B.Ma=new A.i("feature_spirit_disruptive_spirit","Disruptive Spirit","Spaces adjacent to your spirit are difficult terrain for enemies. You and your allies have a +1 to attacks and status checks against enemies adjacent to your spirit. This doesn't include your spirit attacks. ")
B.Ka=new A.i("feature_spirit_horrifying_spirit","Horrifying Spirit","When an enemy starts range {Half Source} of your spirit, Make an Status Check vs Wis, On Success, Deal {Half Source d6} damage.")
B.Mp=new A.i("feature_spirit_soothing_spirit","Soothing Spirit","When your allies start their turn within 1 of the spirit or enters within 1 of the spirit for the first time during their turn, they gain {half Source d6} shield.")
B.Vo=s([B.Ma,B.Ka,B.Mp],t.U)
B.Nm=new A.a8("feature_spirit","Spirit","[Action] Target an unoccupied square within 6 spaces, and summon your Spirit. As long as you remain concentrating, When you use the ability and as a [Reaction] on following turns, you may move your spirit Companion up to 6 spaces ignoring Difficult terrain, and make a Melee Attack vs Wis targeting enemies range 1. On Success Deal {Source d10} Damage ignoring shields and resistance. \n\nYour Spirit can be anything as long but takes up the space of a medium creature. It uses your defenses when attacked, and you take half of all damage that would be dealt to the spirit. This damage cannot be reduced in any way. You do not make concentration checks from damage to your companion. Allies and the spirit may flank.\n\n[Reaction] During your turn, spend your reaction and summon your spirit in an unoccupied space within 6\n",B.r,B.Vo,!1)
B.IU=new A.i("feature_stance_crane","Crane","When you are targeted by a Melee attack and are not prone, You may make an attack instead of a defense. On success, Deal {Half Source d6} Damage and the attack misses as normal. On failure, you fall prone and the attack succeeds against you")
B.HV=new A.i("feature_stance_dog","Dog","While prone, melee attacks do not have advantage against you and you don\u2019t have disadvantage making melee attacks. When you succeed on a melee attack using your action when prone, deal {Half Source d6} Extra damage.")
B.KE=new A.i("feature_stance_defensive","Defensive","When you enter the stance gain {Source d6} Shield. When you succeed on an Attack using your action, gain {Half Source d6} Shield.")
B.N3=new A.i("feature_stance_cat","Cat","When you enter the stance, Dash {Source} or stand from prone. When you Succeed on an attack using your action when not prone, dash {half Source}.")
B.N1=new A.i("feature_stance_dueler","Dueler\u2019s","When you Succeed on an attack using your action and you & the target do not have any allies adjacent to them or are grappling, Deal {Half Source d6} extra damage.")
B.J5=new A.i("feature_stance_horse","Horse","On Success with an attack using your action, you cannot be pushed or knocked prone until the start of your next turn.")
B.JK=new A.i("feature_stance_reckless","Reckless","You have advantage on Attacks, and Disadvantage on Defenses.")
B.Mj=new A.i("feature_stance_bleed","Bleed","When you succeed on a Melee attack using your action, give the target\u2019s {Half Source}d6 Bleed. After Activating, Your next Melee attack gives {Source}d6 Bleed instead.")
B.Ih=new A.i("feature_stance_cold","Cold","When you succeed on a Melee attack using your action, give the targets 1 cold. After Activating, Your next Melee attack gives 2 instead.")
