B.NL=new A.a8("feature_sting","Sting","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Dex Targeting an enemy range 2, On a Success, deal {Source d6} Damage and then make an Status Check vs Vit, On Success, deal {Source d8} extra Damage. \n\n[Reaction] when an enemy starts it turn or becomes range 2, spend your reaction and make a Status Check vs Vit. On Success deal {Source d8} damage.\n",B.r,B.U9,!1)
B.MS=new A.i("feature_storm_gusty","Gusty","While concentrating, All spaces in range of the storm cost 1 more speed to move into for all creatures excluding you.")
B.Kt=new A.i("feature_storm_violent","Violent","While concentrating, each time you succeed on making the storm attack, increase the damage by 1.")
