B.Op=new A.a8("feature_storm","Storm","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Wis. On Success, Deal {Source d6} damage to all enemies range 3 and you may concentrate on storm. While concentrating, At the start of your turn, deal {Half Source d6} damage to enemies range 3.\n\n[Reaction] After you or an ally fails to concentrate, Spend your reaction and make a Ranged Attack vs Wis. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage to enemies range 3 of the triggering character.\n",B.r,B.WN,!1)
B.Im=new A.i("feature_stunning_palm_gentle_way","Gentle Way","You gain advantage on the attack, but the attack doesn\u2019t deal damage.")
B.Ly=new A.i("feature_stunning_palm_heart_stop","Heart Stop","Instead of stunning the enemy, you may Stop their heart instead. As long as you remain concentrating, On the start of their turn, Make an Status Check Vs Vit, On a Success, deal {Source d6} Damage and the target is stunned. On a miss, the effect ends and the target ends its turn taking {Power} Damage.")
B.Ii=new A.i("feature_stunning_palm_two_handed","Two Handed","You make 2 attacks against the target instead of 1. Both attacks must be against the same target.")
B.Ub=s([B.Im,B.Ly,B.Ii],t.U)
B.Nr=new A.a8("feature_stunning_palm","Stunning Palm","[Action: 1 Unarmed]: Make an Attack Vs Vit targeting an enemy range 1. On Success, they take {Source d6} Damage and are stunned until the start of your next turn. \n\n[Reaction] When an enemy starts or becomes range 1, Spend your reaction, and make your stunning palm action against the triggering enemy.\n",B.r,B.Ub,!1)
B.Me=new A.i("feature_swallow_feed","Feed","When a target of your swallow dies, You may heal yourself or an adjacent ally {Source d6}. The body of the target may not be consumed by the Consume ability.")
B.MC=new A.i("feature_swallow_digest","Digest","While Concentrating on Swallow, [Action] Make an Status Check Vs Vit against the Target of your swallow. On Success: Deal {Source d12} Damage.")
B.N4=new A.i("feature_swallow_tongue","Tongue","You may target an enemy range 4 and the attack targets Dex instead. On a Success, pull them to a space adjacent to you before swallowing them.")
B.Vn=s([B.Me,B.MC,B.N4],t.U)
B.Oa=new A.a8("feature_swallow","Swallow","[Action] Target 1 enemy your size or smaller range 1, and Make a Melee Attack vs Str, On Success: While you remain concentrating, You swallow the target. While swallowed, they are stunned, and they may not be targeted by any ability or effect. On the start of their turn, Make an Status Check vs Str, On Success: Deal {Source d6} Damage. On Failure, They end their turn climbing free and the effect ends. While Concentrating, If the target is your size, you cannot move, and if they are smaller than you, you move at half speed.\n\n[Reaction] At the end of an enemy turn who is range 1, spend your reaction, and make your Swallow action against the triggering enemy.\n",B.r,B.Vn,!1)
B.IY=new A.i("feature_subjugation_Blood_pact","Blood pact","the target gains {Half Source} d6 bleed. Every time they take this bleed damage you and the target gain shield equal to the bleed damage.")
B.Kp=new A.i("feature_subjugation_Choke_Chain","Choke Chain","Until the start of the target's next turn, at the end of your turn, if the target isn't within range 3 of you, dash them to a free space within 3. After any effect that moves you, if the target isn't within 3, dash them to a free space within 3.")
B.IT=new A.i("feature_subjugation_Whipped","Whipped","until the end of the situation the target takes and deals an additional 1d8 damage from subjugation for every time they have been targeted by subjugation in this Situation up to a max of {Level d8}. Until the end of the encounter the target gets a bonus to healing equal to 1d8 for every time they have been targeted by subjugation up to {Level d8}. ")
B.Ws=s([B.IY,B.Kp,B.IT],t.U)
B.O2=new A.a8("feature_subjugation","Subjugation","[Reaction] At the start of a consenting ally range 3\u2019s turn, Spend your reaction and deal {Half Source d6} damage to them ignoring shield and damage reduction. Until the end of their next turn, as long as they are within 3 spaces of you, they deal {Half Source d12} extra damage on attacks and gain resistance against attacks that target Int, Wis, or Cha.\n\n[Reaction] When a consenting ally range {Source} gets problems on a check, spend your reaction, and they reroll the check with a +1 to success and they take {Half Source d6} damage ignoring shield and damage reduction. Until their next turn, as long as they are within 3 spaces of you, gain damage Resistance against attacks that target Int, Wis, or Cha.\n",B.T,B.Ws,!1)
B.Lw=new A.i("feature_taze_Ark","Ark","After attacking, attack another creature within 2 spaces Vs Vit. On Success, They take {Source d8} Damage, and the enemy falls prone, and may not make opportunity attacks until the start of your next turn.")
B.Mh=new A.i("feature_taze_Conduct","Conduct","On Success, Deal half damage to each adjacent enemy. Those enemies cannot make opportunity attacks until the start of next turn.")
B.L0=new A.i("feature_taze_Charging Cable","Charging Cable","On the Start of your next turn, if the target of taze remained within range 3 of you since you used it, Make a Melee Attack Vs Vit. On Success, they take {Source d10} Damage, and the enemy falls prone, and may not make opportunity attacks until the start of your next turn. Note: The target of Arch is unaffected by this.")
B.WM=s([B.Lw,B.Mh,B.L0],t.U)
B.Nh=new A.a8("feature_taze","Taze","[Action] Make a Melee Attack Vs Vit Targeting 1 enemy Range 3. On Success, they take {Source d10} Damage, and the enemy falls prone, and may not make opportunity attacks until the start of your next turn.\n\n[Reaction] During Ally Turns, Spend your reaction, and make your taze action from the triggering ally\u2019s space.\n",B.r,B.WM,!1)
B.LV=new A.i("feature_tentacle_Slamming","Slamming","When you release the target at the start of your next turn, you may spend your [Reaction] Make Melee attack vs Dex against 1 enemy range 3, on success deal {Source d12} bludgeoning damage to the target and grabbed enemy. You may target a free space instead of an enemy to deal damage to just the held enemy.")
B.MF=new A.i("feature_tentacle_Tossing","Tossing","when the target stops being grabbed by the tentacle you may knock them prone and force them to move {Source} to a free space. If you have slamming, do this after slamming.")
B.Hv=new A.i("feature_tentacle_Sucking","Sucking","On success, when the target stops being grabbed, deal {vitality d6} damage and heal for an equal amount.")
