B.O3=new A.a8("feature_tentacle","Tentacle","[Action] Make a Melee Attack vs Wis Targeting 1 enemy range 4. On Success, they take {Source d6} Damage and the target is grabbed by the tentacle until the start of your next turn. While grabbed they are restrained and you may place them in any free space range 3 of you. Whenever you move, you may move the target to a free space range 3 of you. \n\n[Reaction] When an enemy ends its turn range 3, Spend your reaction and make your tentacle attack against the triggering enemy.\n",B.r,B.Wk,!1)
B.KU=new A.i("feature_telekinesis_Dancing_Weapon","Dancing Weapon","While concentrating and wielding a weapon, your weapon remains in a free space range {source} of you and prevents enemies from entering the space. You may make opportunity attacks from the dancing weapons space, as well as triggering Weapon Technique [Reactions].")
B.Ju=new A.i("feature_telekinesis_Crushing","Crushing","While concentrating, [Action] make a ranged attack vs Vit targeting 1 enemy you can see. On success deal {Source d12} damage.")
B.IV=new A.i("feature_telekinesis_Mastermind","Mastermind","While concentrating, when you succeed on a skill check using your action, give {Source d6} shield to an ally range {Source}.")
B.VZ=s([B.KU,B.Ju,B.IV],t.U)
B.NQ=new A.a8("feature_telekinesis","Telekinesis","[Reaction] During your turn, Spend your reaction, As long as you remain concentrating, when you use your [Action] for skills, item interaction, and abilities, you may use a free space within {Source} as the origin.\n\n[Reaction] At the Start of an enemy\u2019s turn that you can see. Make a Melee Attack vs Int. On Success, deal {Source d6} and reduce the target\u2019s speed by {Half Source}.\n",B.r,B.VZ,!1)
B.HE=new A.i("feature_tower_Escape_Pods","Escape Pods","When the Tower is Destroyed, you or allies inside may immediately dash to a free space within {Source} instead of making a Dex defense. After you succeed with your reaction status check, dash to a free space within {Source}.")
B.MZ=new A.i("feature_tower_Sniper_Nest","Sniper's Nest","While in the tower, making attacks at long range doesn\u2019t impose disadvantage when attacking.")
B.Hz=new A.i("feature_tower_Rigged_To_Blow","Rigged To Blow","When the tower is destroyed, Target each enemy range 2 of the tower and make a Status Check vs Dex. On Success, deal {Source d8} damage.")
B.U7=s([B.HE,B.MZ,B.Hz],t.U)
B.OC=new A.a8("feature_tower","Tower","[Action] Create a Wall as if you had used a skill. As long as the wall remains, you and your allies may enter the wall, and gain a {half Source} bonus to range while inside. Creatures inside may not be targeted by attacks from enemies within {Half Source} of the tower, but such enemies can still attack the tower itself. When the tower is destroyed, creatures inside must make a Dex defense or fall prone.\n\n[Reaction] After you succeed on a Melee Attack, Make a Status Check vs Str. On Success, Trap one of the targets in a Tower that is a wall created as if you had used a skill. The target is restrained as long as the tower remains, cannot use reactions, and cannot target anything but the tower and has disadvantage on attacks against the tower.\n",B.T,B.U7,!1)
B.J7=new A.i("feature_the_end_Angelic_Rally","Angelic Rally","On Success, target {Half source} allies in the situation and heal them {Source d6}.")
B.LH=new A.i("feature_the_end_Martyr","Martyr","On Success, you may increase the damage to {Source d12} and you are also targeted. The damage against you ignores your resistance and shield.")
B.Ku=new A.i("feature_the_end_Retribution","Retribution","On Success, until the start of your next turn [Reaction] when the target damages one of your allies, you may spend your reaction to give the ally resistance to the damage and make a status check vs Cha. On success deal {Source d6} damage.")
B.WD=s([B.J7,B.LH,B.Ku],t.U)
B.P4=new A.a8("feature_the_end","The End","[Action] Make a Ranged Attack vs Cha targeting {Half Source} enemies in the situation. On Success, Deal {Source d6} Damage. \n\n[Reaction] At the end of the round, Spend your reaction and trigger your The End action.\n",B.r,B.WD,!1)
B.KS=new A.i("feature_thorns_Root","Root","As long as you are concentrating on thorns, At the end of the target\u2019s turn, if the target hasn't moved on their turn, the thorns grow 1 space outward up to {1 + Source}. If an enemy makes any Attack in the thorn growth, they take the damage. Whenever the target moves or dashes they lose the roots. ")
B.L9=new A.i("feature_thorns_Burs","Burs","After an enemy takes damage from your thorns, make an Status Check vs Wis, On a Success, the target has Burs, reducing their speed by {half Source}. On the Start of the target\u2019s turn, repeat the Status Check, On Success, deal {Source d6} damage and if you Miss, the effect ends.")
B.LL=new A.i("feature_thorns_Blood_Rose","Blood Rose","Whenever your thorns deal damage to an enemy, heal the attacked target of your thorns equal to the damage dealt by the thorns.")
B.Tf=s([B.KS,B.L9,B.LL],t.U)
B.Oy=new A.a8("feature_thorns","Thorns","[Action] Target a creature range 1. As long as you are concentrating, the target gains Resistance to damage from Melee Attacks. When the target succeeds on a defense caused by a Melee Attack, deal {Half Source d6} damage to the attacker. While concentrating, if you activate the ability again, you may add the new targets to your current concentration.\n\n[Reaction] During your turn, spend your reaction and trigger your thorns action.\n\n[Reaction] After an ally Succeeds on a Defense from a Melee Attack, Make a Status Check vs Wis. On Success, Deal {Source d6} damage.\n",B.T,B.Tf,!1)
B.IK=new A.i("feature_throw_Counter_Throw","Counter Throw","Passive: When making an attack of opportunity, you may use your Throw action instead.")
B.JH=new A.i("feature_throw_Bounce_Off","Bounce Off","If you could throw the target onto an obstacle or into a wall, place them adjacent to it and deal {Source d6} extra damage.")
B.Jf=new A.i("feature_throw_Hold_on","Hold on","On Success, You may throw the target to a free space within {Source} then you dash to a free space adjacent to the target.")
B.UN=s([B.IK,B.JH,B.Jf],t.U)
B.ND=new A.a8("feature_throw","Throw","[Action: 1 Unarmed]: Make a Melee Attack vs Str targeting an enemy within 1, who is no more than 1 size bigger than you: On a Success, you may throw them to a free space within {2*Source} of you and deal {Source d10} Damage. When you throw an ally, they may make a Finesse to ignore the damage, otherwise they take half damage.\n\n[Reaction] When a character starts or becomes range 1 during its turn, spend your reaction and trigger your throw action against the target.\n",B.r,B.UN,!1)
B.Li=new A.i("feature_tribal_elder_Sage","Sage","After using Treatment Advice or as a [Reaction] during your turn, you may begin concentrating on sage. While concentrating sage reduce your speed by {Half Source}, and allies within {Source} of you get a +1 bonus to defense results.")
B.Jv=new A.i("feature_tribal_elder_Surgeon","Surgeon","When you succeed on coordinated Aid, you end any burn or bleed the target has, if they had none heal {Source d12} instead. After using Treatment Advice, if the target had burn or bleed, make a status check and on success end the burn or bleed. If both or multiple different burns you may only end 1 effect.")
B.Ix=new A.i("feature_tribal_elder_Teacher","Teacher","Allies within {Half Source} of you gain +1 to Coordinated Aid Status Checks. After you use Coordinate Aid, Until the start of your next turn, allies range {Source} of you may spend their [Reaction] during their turn or any allies turn to Target 1 ally range 1 and make a status check. On Success, they heal the target {Targets vitality d6} or give the target the same amount of shield. They may target themselves, but must make the check with disadvantage.")
B.Xc=s([B.Li,B.Jv,B.Ix],t.U)
B.NV=new A.a8("feature_tribal_elder","Tribal Elder","Coordinated Aid [Action]: Target {Half Source} allies range 6 and each target may choose 1 ally range 1 and make a status check. On success, either Heal the ally {Source d6} or grant them {Source d6} shield, healers choice. You may target yourself. A target may heal themselves but must make the status check with disadvantage.\n\nTreatment Advice: [Reaction] When an ally range {Source} fails a defense against a status check, spend your reaction, and the target rerolls the check with a +1 to results.\n",B.T,B.Xc,!1)
B.L_=new A.i("feature_tribal_gatherer_Hold_this","Hold this","After using any [Reaction] that triggers because an ally, the ally may give you any item they are carrying.")
B.Ke=new A.i("feature_tribal_gatherer_Nomadic","Nomadic","After using Coordinated Movement, Retreat, or Work, At the end of the round, you and allies range {Source} may move up to {Source}.")
B.Kb=new A.i("feature_tribal_gatherer_Communication","Communication","When you use Coordinated Work, each ally in range also gains 1 reroll for that same skill. ")
B.V8=s([B.L_,B.Ke,B.Kb],t.U)
B.Oj=new A.a8("feature_tribal_gatherer","Tribal Gatherer","Coordinated Movement [Reaction]: When you or an ally you can see Uses [Run], you may spend your reaction, you and allies range {Source} may immediately move up to their speed.\n\nCoordinated Retreat: [Reaction] When you or an ally you can see Uses [Retreat], you may spend your reaction, you and allies range {Source} may immediately move up to half their speed without provoking.\n\nCoordinated Work [Reaction]: When an ally range {Source} uses an action to make a skill check, you may spend your reaction, to give them 1 reroll and 1 additional reroll per ally within {Half Source} of the target. These rerolls can only be used on that specific skill and last until the end of the situation.\n",B.T,B.V8,!1)
B.N7=new A.i("feature_tribal_hunter_Packhunter","Packhunter","Coordinated strike: When you or allies target the same target gain a +1 to attack results. Joint strike, when you target the same target as the triggering ally, gain a +1 to the attack results.")
B.Lb=new A.i("feature_tribal_hunter_Leader_of_the_Hunt","Leader of the Hunt","After Coordinated Strike or Joint Strike, Until the start of your next turn, allies within {source} spaces of you have +1 to attack results.")
B.J4=new A.i("feature_tribal_hunter_Gather_and_Prepare","Gather and Prepare","[Action] You and all Allies range {source} may move up to {source} spaces, then may make a conceal check to hide. Until the end of your next turn, you and your allies have a +1 to Coordinated Strike attack results.")
B.TV=s([B.N7,B.Lb,B.J4],t.U)
B.NG=new A.a8("feature_tribal_hunter","Tribal Hunter","Coordinated Strike [Action]: You and {Source/3} allies range 6 make either a Ranged Attack vs Dex Range 6 or Melee Attack vs Str range 1 targeting one enemy, on success deal {Source d6} damage for Ranged, and {Source d8} for melee. Each attacker chooses range or melee individually.\n\nJoint Strike [Reaction] After an Ally you can see makes an attack during their turn, Spend your reaction and you and {Source/3} allies you can see either make a Ranged Attack vs Dex Range 6 or Melee Attack vs Str range 1 targeting one enemy. On Success, for ranged deal {Source d6} damage, and for Melee deal {Source d8} damage. Each attacker choose ranged or melee individually.\n",B.r,B.TV,!1)
B.KG=new A.i("feature_upgrade_armor_Self_Walking_Legs","Self Walking Legs"," At the start of your turn, You may force targets to move {Source}.")
B.Hw=new A.i("feature_upgrade_armor_Drone_Delivered","Drone Delivered","You may target Creatures range {2 * Source} and when you use the feature, you may force them to move to a free space range {Source}.")
B.KP=new A.i("feature_upgrade_armor_Power_Armor","Power Armor","While concentrating, Each round, the target may gain resistance to the damage from an attack up to {Half Source} times.")
B.VR=s([B.KG,B.Hw,B.KP],t.U)
B.Ny=new A.a8("feature_upgrade_armor","Upgrade Armor","[Reaction] During your turn or when an ally becomes adjacent to you, Spend your reaction and Target {Half Source} creature without upgraded armor range 1. As long as you remain concentrating, they gain a +1 bonus to defense results. While concentrating, if you activate the ability again, you may add the new targets to your current concentration.\n\n[Reaction] Start of a Combat Situation when you were not surprised, you may spend your reaction and give up to {Half Source} Creatures on your team your upgraded armor, and you begin concentrating on your upgraded armor. You do not regain your reaction on your first turn.\n",B.T,B.VR,!1)
B.HD=new A.i("feature_upgrade_attacks_Extender","Extender","Increase the target's attack range by {Half Source}.")
B.M9=new A.i("feature_upgrade_attacks_Magical","Magical","The targets may choose to have their attacks target Int, Wis, or Cha defense instead. If they do, they deal 1d12 extra damage.")
B.UC=s([B.HD,B.M9],t.U)
B.O8=new A.a8("feature_upgrade_attacks","Upgrade Attacks","[Reaction] During your turn or when an ally becomes adjacent to you, Spend your reaction and Target {Half Source} creatures with unupgraded attacks Range 1. As long as you remain concentrating, they gain a +1 to attack results and deal {Half Source d6} extra damage on success. While concentrating, if you activate the ability again, you may add the new targets to your current concentration.\n\n[Reaction] Start of a Combat Situation when you were not surprised, you may spend your reaction and give up to {Half Source} Creatures on your team your Attack upgrade, and you begin concentrating on your upgraded attacks. You do not regain your reaction on your first turn.\n",B.T,B.UC,!1)
B.Ja=new A.i("feature_vow_My_Valor","My Valor","While concentrating, If the target is within {Source} of you, they have +1 to attack results.")
B.Ms=new A.i("feature_vow_Shared_My_Blood","My Blood","While concentrating, At the start of your turn or when you take your vow, you may gain up to {Source} d6 bleed. As long as you have this bleed, your vow target has the same amount of regeneration. Damage from this bleed doesn\u2019t require you to make concentration checks.")
B.Nd=new A.i("feature_vow_My_Vengeance","My Vengeance","While Concentrating, you deal {Source/3} d8 bonus damage to any enemy that has damaged the target of your vow in this situation.")
B.HS=new A.i("feature_vow_My_Friends","My Friends","You may target any number of your allies.")
B.Ig=new A.i("feature_vow_My_Heart","My Heart","While concentrating, you give half of the healing and shield you receive to your vow target, reducing your healing and shield by the same amount. If you or your vow target die, the other must make a Will Defense, On Success they take {Half Vitality d12} damage. On Problems, they take {Vitality d12} damage.")
B.Ve=s([B.Ja,B.Ms,B.Nd,B.HS,B.Ig],t.U)
B.OK=new A.a8("feature_vow","Vow","[Reaction] During your Turn, or Start of the Encounter, target 1 of your allies and begin concentrating on your vow. While concentrating, the target has resistance to all damage and you take an equal amount of damage whenever they take damage. Damage from your vow doesn\u2019t require you to make concentration checks. \n\n[Action] Target 1 of your allies and begin concentrating on your vow.\n",B.T,B.Ve,!1)
B.IF=new A.i("feature_wall_of_shields_Champion","Champion","You automatically succeed on concentration checks caused by attacks against your allies and you gain resistance to damage from attacks that targeted your allies.")
B.HP=new A.i("feature_wall_of_shields_Empowered","Empowered","You and your allies adjacent to the wall gain {Half Source} bonus range on attacks.")
B.HA=new A.i("feature_wall_of_shields_Tactician","Tactician","While Concentrating, [Reaction] During your turn, You may move {Source} spaces then reshape your wall.")
B.VO=s([B.IF,B.HP,B.HA],t.U)
B.Nl=new A.a8("feature_wall_of_shields","Wall of Shields","[Action] Summon {Source} spaces worth of shield walls in free spaces that are connected to your space. The walls last as long as you remain concentrating. Characters cannot move through the walls but may dash over. Whenever your wall is attacked, you are attacked instead. When a character targets an ally on the other side of the wall or the ally is adjacent to the wall, you may have the attack instead target your wall. While concentrating, you are restrained and at the end of your turn you gain {Source d6} shield.\n\n[Reaction] During your or a willing ally's turn, spend your reaction. Perform your shield wall using the triggering ally instead of yourself but You concentrate on the wall instead of the target. The target may stop the wall at any time.  \n",B.T,B.VO,!1)
B.JA=new A.i("feature_ward_Banish","Banish","Whenever you succeed a Ward Status Check, you also push enemies adjacent to you {Half Source} spaces away from you.")
B.Iz=new A.i("feature_ward_Enchant","Enchant","You may force the targets to move {Source} spaces instead of pushing them. Including from Banish.")
B.LN=new A.i("feature_ward_Safety","Safety","While Concentrating, the target gains advantage on defenses from Opportunity Attacks. The Target of your Ward Reaction gains advantage on defenses from Opportunity Attacks until the end of their turn.")
B.Vr=s([B.JA,B.Iz,B.LN],t.U)
B.Oi=new A.a8("feature_ward","Ward","[Action] Target yourself or an Ally range 4 and begin concentrating. While concentrating, at the start of the target\u2019s turn make a Status Check vs Wis. On Success, the target gains {Source d6} shield, and push all enemies adjacent to the target {half Source} spaces away from the target.\n\n[Reaction] At the start of your or an ally\u2019s turn, Make a status check vs Wis. On Success, give the Target {Source d6} shield, and push enemies adjacent to the target {half Source} Spaces away from the target.\n",B.T,B.Vr,!1)
