B.Ox=new A.a8("feature_wave","Wave","[Action] target all enemies within a {Source}x{Source} box with at least 1 space adjacent to you and Make an Melee Attack vs Str. On success, deal {Source d8} damage and push them up to {Source} in the same direction.\n\n[Reaction] During your or ally turns, Spend your reaction, Make a Melee Attack Vs Str targeting all enemies in a {Source}x{Source} box with at least 1 space adjacent to the Triggering character. On success, deal {Source d8} and push them up to {Source} in the same direction.\n",B.r,B.WZ,!1)
B.Jl=new A.i("feature_weapon_attack_Charge","Charge","Before making a Melee Weapon attack, Move up to {2*Source} in a straight line toward the target. If you moved at least 2 spaces, gain a +1 to the attack result.")
B.N8=new A.i("feature_weapon_attack_culling","Culling","When you kill an enemy, You may make an attack with a weapon you are holding dealing {Source d6} extra damage on a Success. The extra culling attack may not trigger a culling attack.")
B.N2=new A.i("feature_weapon_attack_penetrating","Penetrating","After you Succeed with a weapon attack, the attack ignores damage Resistance and Shield.")
