B.Oz=new A.a8("feature_whirlwind","Whirlwind","[Action]: Make a Melee attack vs Dex Targeting enemies range 2. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage, and you may dash any enemies in range to a free space in range. \n\n[Reaction] During your or allies turns, spend your reaction and make a whirlwind attack. \n",B.r,B.W_,!1)
