B.KD=new A.i("feature_wreath_of_flames_Living_Inferno","Living Inferno","The target gains {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Dex. If you target an ally, they have {Half Source} d12 regeneration as long as they have this burn.")
B.Iv=new A.i("feature_wreath_of_flames_Thorn_Wreath","Thorn Wreath","Whenever the target fails a melee defense, both the target and the attacker gain {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Dex. Allies do not gain this burn.")
B.Vt=s([B.JF,B.KD,B.Iv],t.U)
B.Nu=new A.a8("feature_wreath_of_flames","Wreath of Flames","[Reaction] During your or an ally turn, Target a creature within 1 space. As long as you are concentrating, whenever an enemy starts their turn within 1 space of the Target, or becomes within 1 space of them for the first time during their turn, make an Status Check Vs Dex. On Success, they gain {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Dex. The target of the wreath of flame doesn\u2019t trigger the status check.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally fails a defense, You may begin concentrating on Wreath of flame targeting the triggering ally. If the triggering defense was from a Melee Attack, give the attacker {Half Source} d6 Burn vs Dex.\n",B.T,B.Vt,!1)
B.LD=new A.i("feature_wraith_Drain","Drain","On success, You or the triggering ally gain {Half Source d6} shield.")
B.L8=new A.i("feature_wraith_Rip","Rip","On Success with the reaction, if the triggering attack also succeeds give the target {Source} d6 bleed.")
B.Ie=new A.i("feature_wraith_Torment","Torment","On Success, until the end of your next turn, the target gets a -1 on defense results while within 3 of you.")
