B.P1=new A.a8("feature_wraith","Wraith","[Action] Dash {Half Source} then make a Melee Attack vs Wis targeting 1 enemy range 3. On Success, deal {Source d6} damage and this damage ignores shield and resistance.\n\n[Reaction] When you or an ally range 6 Make a Melee attack during their turn, spend your reaction and make a Melee Attack vs Wis. On success, Deal {Source d6} damage, and this damage ignores Shield and Resistance. \n",B.r,B.WQ,!1)
