B.a3A=new A.dj("source_innate","Innate","The character can use the ability as much as they like, using a Source value of {Half Power}. If the feature only has the innate source gain +1 to the source value.","If you only have innate as your only source, gain +1 to skill results.","{Half Power}",B.BS,!1,null,null,B.fY,null,4289979900)
